001package com.pingidentity.sdk.pingonewallet.appevents;
002
003public abstract class AppEvent {
004
005    transient String event;
006    String value;
007    AppEventType type;
008
009    public AppEvent(String event, AppEventType type, String value) {
010        this.event = event;
011        this.value = value;
012        this.type = type;
013    }
014
015    public void setEvent(String event) {
016        this.event = event;
017    }
018
019    public void setValue(String value) {
020        this.value = value;
021    }
022
023    public void setType(AppEventType type) {
024        this.type = type;
025    }
026
027    public String getEvent() {
028        return event;
029    }
030
031    public String getValue() {
032        return value;
033    }
034
035    public AppEventType getType() {
036        return type;
037    }
038}
